AnnotationAssertion(<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/wikidataMatch> <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/MilliM> <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q174789>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:isDefinedBy <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/MilliM> <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://qudt.org/vocab/unit/MilliM> "Millimeter"@de)
